                android:text="Good for: Arms\nDescription: While sitting down, stretch your arms out at your sides and press your shoulder blades together. With your palms facing down, circle your arms forwards around 20 times. Then, face your palms upwards and circle your arms backwards around 20 times. After this, circle your wrists 20 times in each direction.
\nTiming: 2 minutes
\nCalories Burned: 15 calories"
                android:textColor="@color/black"
                android:textSize="17dp"
                android:textStyle="italic" />

