\nDescription: Find an empty space, such as a meeting room or corridor and try lunging as you walk. You can use tables and chairs for support if needed.
\nTiming: 15 Minutes
\nCalories Burned:137 calories"
                android:textColor="@color/black"
                android:textSize="17dp"
                android:textStyle="italic" />

