\nDeception: Position yourself on the very edge of your desk with your palms placed on either side of you and your feet flat on the floor. Bend at the elbow and lower yourself towards the floor until your elbows are bent at 90 degrees, aim to hold the pose for 30 seconds.
\nTiming: 5 mins
\nCalories Burned: 20 calories
"
                android:textSize="17dp"
                android:background="@color/underline"
                android:textColor="@color/black"
                android:textStyle="italic" />

